          "y": 930,
          "name": "note",
          "width": 1440,
          "height": 130,
          "content": "FRAME 6 \u2014 COLLAPSED top level (md:w-14 / 56px). The fix for #4810: at 56px every label is dropped, only icons remain centered in the rail. Top\u2192bottom: brand mark (S) + expand chevron (chevrons-right restores w-56); workspace identity as ICONS ONLY \u2014 gold org avatar (S, gold-bordered) + repo dot (git-branch glyph) \u2014 NEVER unmounts (TR1 / ADR-047 circuit breaker); icon-only primary nav (Dashboard active / KB / Analytics); footer = theme toggle + Status + Settings + Sign out. Hover any item \u2192 tooltip pill recovers the hidden text label (a11y: identity stays discoverable). The 'Working on: jikig-ai/soleur' string is NOT crushed into the strip \u2014 it is recovered on hover only."
        }
      ]
