              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "zt0082",
                  "content": "Collapsed + drilled: the tree auto-expands as a peek panel",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "fill": "$text-primary",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "fontWeight": "600"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "zt0083",
                  "content": "At 56px the secondary tree cannot legibly collapse to icons (folders and files are indistinguishable as glyphs). Rather than crush it, drilling into a section auto-expands an attached 200px tree-peek panel anchored to the icon spine. The collapse chevron is replaced by a pin: unpinning returns to the icon spine; the spine itself keeps the identity icons mounted.",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "fill": "$text-secondary",
                  "fontSize": 14
                }
              ]
            }
